name: Lust and Deception
description:
Don't believe what you see. No others can save you but yourself.

In this evolving world not only convenience is evolving, but digital scam as well.
Digital fraud has existed since the birth of the internet, from virus attacks to fraud under the guise of helps, by exploiting the lust for instant wealth and convenience. This work is dedicated to raising awareness of online fraud and digital scams.
